# Third-party submodules (ignore content but keep git tracking if they are submodules)
# Note: submodules are tracked by git, but if they are just folders, ignore them.
# Since they are submodules, we generally don't ignore them in the root .gitignore 
# unless we want to hide untracked content inside them.
# However, we can ignore common large artifact directories that might appear in root.

